root: ^Aunt Judy's diary. Let's hear what happened next.
^"Hector quit today. I guess the records flying off the wall did it finally."
^"I can't blame him one bit - it's not like we have any customers anyway."
^"I keep hearing strange beats from the back storeroom."
^"Managing this store is a battle. I'll go on the record saying that."
^Aunt Judy really was struggling, wasn't she? I have to know what happened next.
^I'll purrsue this to the very end!
